message: Hello Bob, I'm excited to present you with our premium product, which is tailored to meet your specific needs and valued at $15000 to you. Considering its exceptional quality and the benefits it offers, I would like to extend an exclusive offer to you. I am proposing to sell this product to you for $14000. This special price is available only to you and is an opportunity not to be missed. Please let me know if you are interested in proceeding with this offer.
